channel.title: Haha i had fun with this one
channel.description:
Opened up gimp last night with a vision :). This is all paths tooling, coloring, paterens and the focal is a render. Took me ages to make it. C&c , comment, w/e. The clock was path tooling and pattern filled, the trash can was path tooling and partern filled even the outlet and the paper on the wall where made from scratch.
[img]http://i255.photobucket.com/albums/hh154/santagfx/tags/scratch.png[/img]
Thanks :D
